========================
====== ACTIVITIES ======
========================

1. Motivation for using activities
-- Foundation for an app
-- A way to categories the different aspects of an app
-- Signify interaction with the user

2. What is an activity
-- An interaction with the user
-- One main activity
-- A host of fragments
-- Activities call each other

3. Navigating between activities
-- Intents
-- Results (startActivityForResult)

4. Life-cycle
-- Creation
-- Destruction
-- Saved instance